<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nt fạdynạ ạlạ̉myn</title>
<aka>ạnt fạdynạ ạlạmyn</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạản̊ta fādīnā ạlạảmīn̊
 ḥubũka lil̊mun̊tahay̱
 ạản̊ta kan̊zunā ạltẖãmīn̊
 wālnãṣību ạl̊musẖ̊tahay̱

[V2]
 2- qad̊ ạảk̊mal̊ta kulã sẖaẙʾiⁿ
 wamaḍaẙta lil̊ʿulạ
 wāảʿ̊ṭaẙta lanā waʿ̊daⁿạ
 ạản̊ tā̊̉tīnā ʿājilạ

[V3]
 3- fahā naḥ̊nu ạlậna nar̊jū
 ạản̊ narāka yā ḥabīb̊
 mal̊qāka lilnãf̊si yaḥ̊lū
 yuf̊riḥu ạl̊qal̊ba ạl̊kayỉyb̊

[V4]
 4- tan̊tahī ʿamãạ qarībi
 kulũ ạảyãạmi ạlsãfar̊
 wakadẖā rajā ạl̊gẖarībi
 yataḥaqãq̊ lilnãẓar̊

[V5]
 5- qad̊ danā ạl̊yaẘma zamānuⁿ
 min̊ qadīmiⁿ yun̊taẓar̊
 kulũ bāriⁿ̃ sayulạqī
 fī ạl̊hawā rabã ạl̊basẖar̊</lyrics>
</song>